      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a reliable daily driver and a weekend showpiece. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple; while the driver\u2019s bolster shows light creasing, the cabin is free of odors, tears, or significant wear. Every toggle and switch functions exactly as intended, including the ice-cold dual-zone climate control and the premium sound system. Mechanically, the car is robust\u2014the engine pulls smoothly through the rev range, and the transmission shifts with crisp precision. Recent preventative maintenance includes a fresh fluid service and a comprehensive inspection of the braking system. It has been garage-kept and comes with a thick binder of service records, offering the next owner complete confidence in its history and performance.",
