      "description": "Presenting a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This driver-spec example is equipped with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive rod bearing service and replacement of both throttle actuators. The suspension retains its sharp response via the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system, and the subframe remains structurally sound. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the powertrain and drivetrain harmonics are excellent, making this an ideal candidate for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical integrity and performance over showroom-floor cosmetics.",
